y could hear the grasshoppers","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0119_R_1.webp","w":686,"h":900,"caption":"Reims Cathedral 1974 Chagall left lancet Virgin & Child","type":"photo"}]},{"seq":9,"place_id":"malaucene-france","lon":5.1321258,"lat":44.1732744,"place":"Malaucène, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The chocolate puddings were delicious.","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0120_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":699,"caption":"Roman Bridge over Ouvèze, Vaison-la-Romaine","type":"photo"},{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0121_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":656,"caption":"Chaource cheese label, Simon's favourite","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":10,"place_id":"grimaud-france","lon":6.5222979,"lat":43.2737698,"place":"Grimaud, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We are in a grove of pines + cork oak. The lower trunk bark has been peeled away. There's a distant view of St. Tropez","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0122_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":604,"caption":"L'Annonciade Museum, Edouard Vuillard 1868-1940, La Soupe d'Annette 1900-1901","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0121_R_1.webp","w":727,"h":242,"caption":"Senequier St Tropez chocolate wrapper","type":"ticket"},{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0121_R_2.webp","w":739,"h":564,"caption":"L'ANNONCIADE musée de Saint-Tropez entry ticket, Picasso Tarif Réduit No 04856","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":11,"place_id":"frejus-france","lon":6.7360182,"lat":43.4330308,"place":"Fréjus, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"main_stop","quote":"The amazing old baptistery at the cathedral, for immersion of adults in the floor","images":[]},{"seq":12,"place_id":"saint-laurent-du-var-france","lon":7.1906969,"lat":43.6690101,"place":"Saint-Laurent-du-Var, 