spel, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We are next to 2 town drunks in a low tent; v. beaten-up face, chain smoking, slumped against a tree","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0127_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":818,"caption":"Villa Ephrussi de Rothschild. Saint-Jean-Cap-Ferrat.","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0127_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":677,"caption":"Madame Ephrussi's bedroom","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":18,"place_id":"cuneo-italy","lon":7.5581367,"lat":44.4580704,"place":"Cuneo, Italy","date":"2007-07-29","role":"main_stop","quote":"Cuneo is still nice - \"style\" Simon said, but dignified.","images":[]},{"seq":19,"place_id":"fenestrelle-italy","lon":7.0495615,"lat":45.0360951,"place":"Fenestrelle, Italy","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"Police arrived at our breakfast table. Once they found out we were English, they were friendly","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0129_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":737,"caption":"Val Chisone: Fortezza di Fenestrelle","type":"postcard"}]},{"seq":20,"place_id":"aussois-france","lon":6.7413988,"lat":45.2275415,"place":"Aussois, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"We've parked over a beautiful view.","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0130_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":763,"caption":"AUSSOIS - Vanoise","type":"postcard"},{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0130_R_1.webp","w":630,"h":900,"caption":"Our walk — hand-drawn route map","type":"map"}]},{"seq":21,"place_id":"saint-rambert-en-bugey-france","lon":5.439958,"lat":45.948607,"place":"Saint-Rambert-en-Bugey, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"The campsite is really lovely, perched high on a valley side, so high that planes fly along the valley below us.","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0131_L_1.webp","w":767,"h":451,"caption":"Eve's chocolate paper from lunch","type":"ticket"}]},{"seq":22,"place_id":"mery-sur-seine-france","lon":3.8913919,"lat":48.5080851,"place":"Méry-sur-Seine, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"chicken & potatoes lashed in cream, 2 cheeses, apricot flan, coffee & chocolate & red wine","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0131_R_1.webp","w":900,"h":439,"caption":"hand-drawn terrain profile with directions","type":"sketch"}]},{"seq":23,"place_id":"longpre-les-corps-saints-france","lon":1.9917431,"lat":50.013403,"place":"Longpré-les-Corps-Saints, France","date":"2007-07-29","role":"overnight_base","quote":"we carried stools into the square & watched the painted facade of Amiens cathedral. It was marvellous, lit up like a jewel, or like an Indian temple.","images":[]},{"seq":24,"place_id":"coquelles-eurotunnel","lon":1.8147,"lat":50.9228,"place":"Coquelles (Eurotunnel)","date":"2007-07-29","role":"crossing_terminal","quote":"A super holiday!","images":[{"src":"media/2007-france-montreuil-reims-provence-malaucene-vaison/B_0134_L_1.webp","w":900,"h":683,"caption":"van above St. Tropez. See A.59","type":"photo"}]}]}